  |       Title : BlazBlue: Cross Tag Battle (Update v1.3.1)                |
  |   -------------------------------------------------------------------   |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Publisher : Arc System Works Co., Ltd   Platform : Nintendo Switch    |
  |   Developer : Arc System Works Co., Ltd     Origin : eShop              |
  |       Genre : Fighting / Action           Title ID : 0100B61008208800   |
